text:
Gmail ist the "final stage" of responsiveness since it will - most likely delete everything what is not inline styled. And since you can't place media queries as inline styling you should create(if not already done) a custom module with your signature and do it something like this

```&lt;Style&gt;
@media and (min-width:480px){
. desktop{
display: block;
mso-hide:none;
}
.mobile {
display: none !important;
mso-hide:all !important;}
}&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;table class="desktop"&gt;
Your desktop signature layout
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;table class="mobile" style="display:block"&gt;
Your mobile signature layout
&lt;/table&gt;```
